# Output Format Templates

## Location for Output Files

All output markdown files should be placed in the `notes/` subfolder of the given draft directory.

Example structure:
```
draft_folder/
├── introduction.tex
├── institutional_setting.tex
├── ...
└── notes/
    ├── copy_edits.md
    ├── ai_screen.md
    └── simplifications.md
```

---

