## Template: ai_screen.md

```markdown
# AI-Specific Punctuation & Structural Tells
**Date:** [date]
**Reviewer:** [name]

Focus: Punctuation-based and structural patterns that flag AI-generated text.

**Target:** 40-50 items total

---

## Quick Checklist

